sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Notebook
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Webhook as Webhook Service<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller
    participant RouteAPI as Route API (OpenShift)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS edge TLS
    participant RayDashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation with OAuth (OpenShift)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS (API Server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated RayCluster
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>RouteAPI: Create Route (ray-dashboard)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service (dashboard)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Secret (mTLS certs)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OAuth Proxy Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    User->>OAuthProxy: GET https://ray-dashboard-{cluster}.{domain}<br/>Auth: OAuth Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>RayDashboard: Forward to 8265/TCP<br/>HTTP (internal pod)
    RayDashboard-->>OAuthProxy: Dashboard HTML
    OAuthProxy-->>User: Response

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 2: AppWrapper Scheduling with Kueue

    participant User2 as User
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant AWController as AppWrapper Controller

    User2->>K8sAPI: POST AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-workload-codeflare-dev-v1beta2-appwrapper<br/>mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result

    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Update AppWrapper status (admitted)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    AWController->>K8sAPI: Watch AppWrapper status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    AWController->>K8sAPI: Create wrapped resources (Jobs, Deployments)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,RayDashboard: Flow 3: Ray Client Connection with mTLS

    participant Client as Ray Client
    participant Route as Ray Client Route<br/>10001/TCP passthrough
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Service<br/>10001/TCP gRPC mTLS

    Client->>Route: gRPC connect<br/>Auth: Client Certificate
    Route->>RayHead: Forward (passthrough TLS)<br/>mTLS handshake
    RayHead-->>Client: Ray cluster API access
